Roxanne McKee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roxanne_McKee 0 Roxanne McKee (born 10 August 1980) is a Canadian actress and model. She is best known for playing Louise Summers in the British soap opera Hollyoaks (2005–2008), Lou Foster in the British drama series Lip Service (2010), Doreah in the British-American fantasy drama series Game of Thrones (2011–2012) and Lady Claire Riesen in the American apocalyptic supernatural series Dominion (2014–2015). She has also starred in films including Wrong Turn 5: Bloodlines (2012), Vendetta (2013) and The Legend of Hercules (2014). Roxanne_McKee ( born_10_August_1980 ) is a_Canadian_actress_and_model .
